snippet.title: Evan and Katelyn Podcast
snippet.description:
A podcast about YouTube stuff, making stuff, and life! It will make sense once you start listening... hopefully. New episodes every Monday!

🛠️ Our main channel is https://www.youtube.com/evanandkatelyn
🎮 We also have a gaming channel https://www.youtube.com/evanandkatelyngaming

Below is our mailing address. If you're a business, please do NOT send unsolicited products:

Evan and Katelyn
215 W Bandera Rd Ste 114-240
Boerne, TX 78006
